## How the Blocks Fit Together
```
Block 1  →  Config & imports
Block 2  →  Load, validate, fill gaps, filter MMA
Block 3  →  Outlier flagging & clipping
Block 4  →  STL per account (parallel) → slope + seasonality features
Block 5  →  Lag, rolling, calendar, cross-product feature assembly
